title: Celebrity Gossip Part 1 - Selena Won't Watch Documentary
description: If your song is going to be stolen without permission… you want it to be stolen by someone with deep pockets right? Well Disney may have stolen a song from an unknown artist. And Selena Gomez says she won’t be watching her documentary when it comes out on Apple TV+.
